WEBVTT

01:27.880 --> 01:29.248
There you go.

01:48.000 --> 01:49.802
You go back to
the fuckin' shelter.

01:49.835 --> 01:52.772
You smell like the fuckin'
third floor of the shelter.

01:52.805 --> 01:56.341
Yeah, we back... we back
in the dressing room now, yeah.

01:56.375 --> 01:58.443
The Commission in here.
They... wrap...

01:58.477 --> 02:00.279
watch-watching 'em wrap
Billy hands.

02:01.513 --> 02:03.849
Yeah, it's all right.

02:16.261 --> 02:17.997
Yeah, but once he gets
in the inside, it's over.

02:18.030 --> 02:19.765
Make that step, it's over.

02:52.497 --> 02:55.768
Yeah. I'll text you
as soon as he's done, okay?

02:55.801 --> 02:57.102
Yeah. I love you, too.

02:57.136 --> 02:58.370
Hi, Jordan.

02:58.403 --> 03:00.039
Okay. Yeah. Do your homework.

03:00.072 --> 03:01.473
Hey, y'all
give him a minute.

03:01.506 --> 03:04.043
- Hey, hey, guys.
- Hey, Mo. What's up?

03:04.076 --> 03:05.377
What's up?

03:05.410 --> 03:07.146
Yeah, let's get out.

03:17.790 --> 03:19.291
Hey.

03:22.928 --> 03:25.564
- Mm-hmm.
- Mm-hmm.

03:25.597 --> 03:27.066
You're ready.

03:28.700 --> 03:31.003
Don't get hit too much.

03:47.386 --> 03:51.256
Hard shots from Darius Jones

03:51.290 --> 03:53.292
to the body and the head,

03:53.325 --> 03:55.594
as he continues putting distance

03:55.627 --> 04:00.299
between himself and Billy Hope
on the scorecards.

04:00.332 --> 04:02.234
This kid Jones is super fast,

04:02.267 --> 04:05.437
and he's killing Billy
with just his left hand.

04:05.470 --> 04:08.340
Jones,
a longer, quicker fighter,

04:08.373 --> 04:10.375
has appeared to win
most of the rounds

04:10.409 --> 04:12.377
to this point in the fight.

04:12.411 --> 04:14.313
Keep them hands up!
Protect that eye!

04:14.346 --> 04:16.648
Come on, chief!
Come on, move!

04:17.950 --> 04:20.119
There you go!

04:20.152 --> 04:23.088
And the crowd comes alive
as Hope lands a right and a left.

04:23.122 --> 04:25.290
Okay, here we go,
here we go.

04:26.992 --> 04:28.928
Good body shots by Hope.

04:28.961 --> 04:30.729
- Dance with me, bitch.
- Let him go.

04:30.762 --> 04:32.031
There he goes
again with that attitude.

04:32.064 --> 04:33.765
He never stops.

04:33.799 --> 04:35.734
It's another
frustrating round for Hope.

04:35.767 --> 04:38.037
He all right.
He ain't hurt him.

04:40.973 --> 04:42.942
It's give and take,
ebb and flow,

04:42.975 --> 04:44.509
here in this fight.

04:44.543 --> 04:46.645
Come on, Billy,
turn the shit back!

04:46.678 --> 04:48.814
As Jones drives him back

04:48.848 --> 04:50.749
- with another uppercut.
- Whoa, good uppercut.

04:50.782 --> 04:52.551
And now Jones again
going to the body...

04:52.584 --> 04:54.253
Come on, baby,
get off those ropes!

04:54.286 --> 04:55.888
...trying to set up the finish

04:55.921 --> 04:57.990
as he drives Hope back
into the ropes again.

04:58.023 --> 05:00.025
I got you, man. I got you.

05:00.059 --> 05:01.861
- Huh? That's all you got?
- Uh-huh.

05:01.894 --> 05:03.996
That's all you got, huh?

05:05.564 --> 05:07.566
Watching,
close to Hope's corner,

05:07.599 --> 05:10.535
his beautiful wife, Maureen,

05:10.569 --> 05:13.672
herself a product
of a Hell's Kitchen orphanage.

05:13.705 --> 05:16.708
- How's the eye?
- Take many more, it's gonna flow.

05:16.741 --> 05:18.543
Yeah, just fix
the fuckin' eye.

05:18.577 --> 05:20.579
State Commission
doctor taking a good look

05:20.612 --> 05:24.216
at Hope's left eye
in the corner.

05:24.249 --> 05:26.285
But the fight will continue.

05:26.318 --> 05:29.088
We've seen Billy Hope
win fights in the past

05:29.121 --> 05:32.457
looking even more the worse
for wear than is the case here.

05:32.491 --> 05:34.293
Nothing has changed tonight.

05:34.326 --> 05:35.995
Seated at ringside,

05:36.028 --> 05:38.563
light heavyweight contender
Miguel "Magic" Escobar,

05:38.597 --> 05:40.365
who would love
to fight the winner.

05:40.399 --> 05:42.601
Okay, keep him on
the end of your stick.

05:42.634 --> 05:44.536
And don't stand
in front of him.

05:44.569 --> 05:47.873
Get yours, relocate. It's like
the bull and the matador.

05:47.907 --> 05:50.575
This is your fuckin' ring.
You're the fuckin' champ, right?

05:50.609 --> 05:52.244
Just go back in and do what
we do; you gotta end this.

05:52.277 --> 05:53.812
Hey, Billy. Billy.

05:53.845 --> 05:56.181
All right, do me a favor
and keep those hands up.

05:56.215 --> 05:58.317
Billy, stay focused.

05:58.350 --> 06:01.253
End it. You don't have time
for this bullshit.

06:01.286 --> 06:02.687
Put an end to this
so we can go the fuck home.

06:02.721 --> 06:04.356
What do you think
I'm trying to do, Eli?

06:04.389 --> 06:05.891
What do you think
I'm trying to do?

06:05.925 --> 06:07.759
Get the shit off my eye!
Let's go! Come on!

06:09.661 --> 06:12.164
Round ten about to begin.

06:17.302 --> 06:19.538
Watch that jab, watch the jab.

06:19.571 --> 06:23.909
Billy Hope still
with that bleeding left eye.

06:23.943 --> 06:28.380
Those who love him would say,
"Defense? What is that?"

06:28.413 --> 06:29.848
- And a hard right cross!
- Yeah, Hope hurt him!

06:29.881 --> 06:31.583
That's it, baby,
that's it.

06:31.616 --> 06:33.352
Good body shot by Darius Jones.

06:33.385 --> 06:34.920
Giving Hope
a little of his medicine,

06:34.954 --> 06:36.788
he comes back to the body
a second time.

06:36.821 --> 06:38.623
He hurt Hope
with that body shot.

06:38.657 --> 06:40.825
Hard right by Hope
drives Jones

06:40.859 --> 06:42.627
back into the ropes.

06:42.661 --> 06:44.396
Let him go. Let him go.

06:44.429 --> 06:45.998
That's one
of the best clean shots

06:46.031 --> 06:48.667
Hope has landed
since the middle of the fight.

06:48.700 --> 06:51.036
And down goes Jones
on a left hook.

06:51.070 --> 06:52.804
Three...

06:52.837 --> 06:55.674
- four, five...
- Tremendous turnaround

06:55.707 --> 06:57.809
in favor of Hope,
here in round ten.

06:57.842 --> 07:00.312
- Come to me, come to me.
- Wow, what a shot!

07:00.345 --> 07:02.247
You stay on him, Billy,
stay on him.

07:02.281 --> 07:04.383
- Are you good? You good? All right.
- I'm good. I'm good.

07:04.416 --> 07:05.951
Tony Weeks is
gonna let him keep fighting.

07:05.985 --> 07:07.852
- Oh!
- But not for long!

07:07.886 --> 07:12.557
And another right hand
may have ended the fight.

07:12.591 --> 07:14.859
...six, seven...

07:14.893 --> 07:15.995
eight...

07:16.028 --> 07:17.462
nine...

07:17.496 --> 07:18.998
That's it.

07:19.031 --> 07:21.633
This is over!

07:21.666 --> 07:24.136
A comeback knockout win
for Billy Hope.

07:24.169 --> 07:27.339
I told you, Jim,
as long as there's a Billy,

07:27.372 --> 07:29.975
there is Hope...
He always has a chance.

07:30.009 --> 07:31.710
So light heavyweight
champ Billy Hope

07:31.743 --> 07:34.113
has a fourth consecutive
title defense

07:34.146 --> 07:36.548
in Madison Square Garden.

07:36.581 --> 07:38.517
Let's go to David Diamante

07:38.550 --> 07:40.819
for the official particulars
on the KO.

07:40.852 --> 07:44.189
Ladies and gentlemen, from
the world's most famous arena,

07:44.223 --> 07:47.792
Madison Square Garden, the
official time of the stoppage:

07:47.826 --> 07:51.930
one minute and 18 seconds
of round number ten.

07:51.963 --> 07:54.266
Your winner by knockout,

07:54.299 --> 07:56.801
still undefeated and still

07:56.835 --> 08:00.005
the undisputed WBC,

08:00.039 --> 08:03.375
WBA, WBO,

08:03.408 --> 08:08.913
and IBF Light Heavyweight
Champion of the World...

08:08.947 --> 08:14.486
Billy "The Great" Hope!

08:14.519 --> 08:18.123
He reminds us of the
great, late Matthew Saad Muhammad.

08:18.157 --> 08:22.294
Just when you think there's no
hope left, here comes Billy.

08:22.327 --> 08:25.030
From an orphanage
in Hell's Kitchen

08:25.064 --> 08:29.268
to a professional career fighting
in Madison Square Garden

08:29.301 --> 08:34.673
is a distance of only a few blocks...
and a million miles.

08:34.706 --> 08:37.775
But it's a journey Billy Hope
has made in his life.

08:37.808 --> 08:40.845
Billy! Billy! Billy!

08:51.490 --> 08:53.125
Hey, Jon Jon,

08:53.158 --> 08:55.460
take the belts out for
the press conference, yeah?

08:55.494 --> 08:58.029
- The new one?
- With the other ones in the back of the car.

08:58.063 --> 08:59.998
Yo, I'll bring that, Mikey.
You bring that one.

09:00.031 --> 09:02.567
- See you at the press conference.
- Come on, Big Mike.

09:02.601 --> 09:05.804
- We got a press conference.
- All right, we'll see you there.

09:08.240 --> 09:09.608
Thanks, Eli.

09:20.852 --> 09:22.087
Hey.

09:22.121 --> 09:24.055
- No.
- I don't know what that is...

09:24.089 --> 09:25.824
- Come here.
- I'm bleeding out of my mouth, baby.

09:25.857 --> 09:27.259
I don't know
when it's coming clean.

09:27.292 --> 09:28.993
What's that, baby?

09:32.497 --> 09:33.932
- What'd you say?
- It's fine, babe.

09:33.965 --> 09:35.367
You want some water?

09:35.400 --> 09:37.802
Yeah. I'm just gonna
take a shower first.

09:37.836 --> 09:39.504
No, no, no.

09:39.538 --> 09:41.039
Can you get
your socks off?

09:41.072 --> 09:42.507
Yourself?

09:42.541 --> 09:44.909
Yeah. I'll just fuckin'
shower in 'em.

09:56.955 --> 09:59.858
Billy!

09:59.891 --> 10:02.594
- Okay, Mike, go ahead.
- Billy, most of us here

10:02.627 --> 10:04.363
had you winning this early.

10:04.396 --> 10:06.131
Were you expecting
such a difficult fight?

10:06.165 --> 10:08.867
Oh. Heh.
Yeah, I don't know, "expect"?

10:08.900 --> 10:11.236
I don't know.
You can't expect anything.

10:11.270 --> 10:14.873
Um, I-I was really looking
forward to just showing up,

10:14.906 --> 10:17.442
walk in the ring, and then
having him fall on the ground.

10:19.344 --> 10:21.045
Billy. Hey, Billy.

10:21.079 --> 10:22.881
No, man, I mean...

10:22.914 --> 10:25.884
I expected a hard fight.
You know? Um...

10:25.917 --> 10:28.253
I put my family
through a lot. Uh...

10:28.287 --> 10:29.888
by the way, Leila,

10:29.921 --> 10:31.523
if you're watching,
go to sleep, baby.

10:33.525 --> 10:35.527
Billy. Hey, Billy, Billy.

10:35.560 --> 10:39.964
Billy. You're 43 and 0... undefeated.
Are you running out of legitimate...

10:39.998 --> 10:42.167
Sorry, can you say that again?

10:42.201 --> 10:44.703
It's impressive.

10:44.736 --> 10:46.905
But who are you gonna fight?
Who are you gonna fight?

10:46.938 --> 10:49.308
- Uh, you know, that's really Jordan and me...
- I think I know one!

10:49.341 --> 10:50.975
Me!

10:53.445 --> 10:56.114
I mean, all the fans around the
world, they want to see it.

10:56.147 --> 10:58.883
Y'all tell me, who else is there?
Your crew knows it.

10:58.917 --> 11:01.052
All these beautiful people
in here know it.

11:01.085 --> 11:04.956
I know it. I just want to know
why you won't give me my shot.

11:04.989 --> 11:06.725
All I want is my shot.
I just want my shot.

11:06.758 --> 11:08.860
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.
Who are you?

11:08.893 --> 11:11.296
You know exactly
who I am, baby.

11:11.330 --> 11:13.965
- He's just trying to make a fight.
- And you're that contender?

11:13.998 --> 11:15.934
You ain't never been hit
by a real man.

11:15.967 --> 11:17.702
All right?

11:17.736 --> 11:20.672
Who's got that...

11:20.705 --> 11:24.008
It's pretty clear that he hasn't
really been hit at all yet, huh?

11:24.042 --> 11:26.177
What are you drinking in that cup, man?

11:26.211 --> 11:27.779
Hey, you know what?
You ain't no champ.

11:27.812 --> 11:29.714
You're all show
and you know that.

11:29.748 --> 11:31.550
Why you so scared
to fight me, Billy?

11:31.583 --> 11:33.718
We all came and gave
a good show tonight,

11:33.752 --> 11:37.222
didn't we, Jordan? Yeah? And I'm pretty
sure we did business, didn't we?

11:37.256 --> 11:39.791
Yeah, all right.
Y'all have a good night, okay?

11:39.824 --> 11:42.327
Sign the contract, baby!

11:42.361 --> 11:45.063
- Gonna be a fight, Billy?
- Just sign the contract, baby!

11:45.096 --> 11:46.798
Is there going to be a fight?

11:46.831 --> 11:49.200
- I want you to line it up!
- Line it up?

11:49.234 --> 11:50.635
Miguel's just
showboating, Billy.

11:50.669 --> 11:52.571
I'm gonna shut him the fuck up.

11:52.604 --> 11:54.773
Line it up.

11:54.806 --> 11:56.875
Turay just makes sense.
If it makes money,

11:56.908 --> 11:58.643
it makes sense. Two for the
bills, one for the belt.

11:58.677 --> 12:00.612
The Turay fight
makes better sense.

12:00.645 --> 12:02.781
No, no, no. You think
Miguel's a better fighter?

12:02.814 --> 12:04.849
No. I didn't say that.
I didn't say that.

12:04.883 --> 12:07.051
What do I got to do? What do
I got to do, say it again?

12:07.085 --> 12:09.120
- You want me to say it again?
- You want to fight me?

12:09.153 --> 12:11.923
Do you want to say it again?
What do you want me to do?

12:11.956 --> 12:13.396
Why do you do this
in front of all...

12:15.494 --> 12:17.161
What happened?

12:17.195 --> 12:20.399
- What's the problem, Billy?
- Hey, yo, yo, I'm sorry.

12:20.432 --> 12:23.001
I'm sorry about that.

12:23.034 --> 12:24.769
- I'll just...
- Don't worry about it. Go on.

12:24.803 --> 12:27.238
- Just, come on, man.
- Don't worry about this.

13:21.192 --> 13:23.628
I want
to get you out of this dress.

13:23.662 --> 13:25.864
Yeah, me, too.
You have no idea.

13:25.897 --> 13:27.332
Hey, Lee,
put those in the office.

13:27.366 --> 13:29.334
- Ugh!
- Come on. Come with me.

13:29.368 --> 13:32.070
- Come with me. Where you going?
- What?

13:32.103 --> 13:34.406
- Come with me.
- Let me put my stuff down.

13:34.439 --> 13:35.840
I got to get
you some ice...

13:35.874 --> 13:37.376
- Leila?
- And some food...

13:37.409 --> 13:38.777
Leila?

13:38.810 --> 13:40.278
Hey, hey. Shh.

13:40.311 --> 13:41.846
She might be sleeping.

13:41.880 --> 13:43.548
- Leila...
- Hey.

13:43.582 --> 13:45.517
- How's it going, Gloria?
- Congratulations, Mr. Billy.

13:45.550 --> 13:47.218
Is she up? Is she up?

13:47.251 --> 13:49.788
Yeah, she's probably
still waiting up for you.

13:49.821 --> 13:52.256
Tell me she didn't
watch that fight.

13:57.261 --> 13:59.063
Oh, I saw you.

13:59.097 --> 14:00.298
I saw you.

14:00.331 --> 14:02.033
Don't try and fool me.

14:02.066 --> 14:04.669
I'm coming for my hug.

14:06.270 --> 14:07.672
Hey, wake up.

14:07.706 --> 14:10.008
Aw! You... Yeah... Oh.

14:10.041 --> 14:11.643
Hi, baby.

14:11.676 --> 14:14.513
Oh, I missed you so much.

14:14.546 --> 14:16.915
I missed you, Daddy.

14:20.184 --> 14:21.420
Can I count?

14:21.453 --> 14:22.887
Mm-hmm.

14:26.357 --> 14:28.326
That's a big one.

14:28.359 --> 14:29.628
Yeah.

14:30.495 --> 14:32.263
Mm.

14:35.133 --> 14:36.334
Eight.

14:36.367 --> 14:37.669
Mm.

14:37.702 --> 14:39.971
- You got hit a lot, Dad.
- Yeah,

14:40.004 --> 14:41.272
you should see the other guy.

14:41.305 --> 14:42.707
No, she should not.

14:42.741 --> 14:44.208
- Aw.
- She needs to go to bed.

14:44.242 --> 14:45.944
And so do you. Come on.

14:45.977 --> 14:48.146
Party's over. Come on.

14:48.179 --> 14:50.214
Why can't I go
see the fights?

14:50.248 --> 14:51.816
Oh, 'cause your mother
thinks they're too...

14:51.850 --> 14:53.518
Why can't she go
to your fights?

14:53.552 --> 14:55.654
Your mom thinks they're
too violent, baby, come on.

14:55.687 --> 14:57.822
But I see stuff like that
on TV all the time.

14:57.856 --> 14:59.658
- I know you do.
- What do you mean?

14:59.691 --> 15:01.125
I watch "The Walking Dead"
with Gloria.

15:01.159 --> 15:02.827
All right,
that's gonna stop.

15:02.861 --> 15:04.663
You, up. Come on,
this is your hint.

15:04.696 --> 15:06.998
- Okay, all right.
- Come on.

15:07.031 --> 15:08.700
Time for bed.
Please... no...

15:08.733 --> 15:10.134
- Dad will let me.
- She has a phone?

15:10.168 --> 15:11.803
She's had a phone
for two months.

15:11.836 --> 15:13.404
Why are you looking at me
like I'm crazy?

15:13.438 --> 15:15.339
'Cause you asked me
to get her the phone?

15:15.373 --> 15:16.908
- Get a ten-year-old a phone?
- Out, out, out.

15:16.941 --> 15:18.376
Do you have
the pass code on it?

15:18.409 --> 15:20.011
Dad would say yes.

15:20.044 --> 15:23.014
Well, sometimes I think
your daddy confuses you

15:23.047 --> 15:25.984
with the other children who
hang around him night and day.

15:26.017 --> 15:27.652
You're talking
about Mikey and Jon Jon, right?

15:27.686 --> 15:29.153
That's right, baby.

15:29.187 --> 15:30.722
Mm...
I love you so much.

15:30.755 --> 15:31.856
I'm serious.

15:31.890 --> 15:33.658
Okay. Come on. Bedtime.

15:33.692 --> 15:35.426
Hey, get away
from my daughter.

15:35.460 --> 15:36.995
You, get out.
Get out.

15:37.028 --> 15:38.597
Go away, Dad.

15:38.630 --> 15:41.666
Good night.

15:41.700 --> 15:43.502
- Hmm?
- Hmm?

15:43.535 --> 15:45.203
What would you like?

15:45.236 --> 15:48.840
I want...
I want to take a break.

15:48.873 --> 15:52.511
I was just thinking we could
maybe blow off the Turay match,

15:52.544 --> 15:54.846
rethink things, pick a fight

15:54.879 --> 15:58.049
- for later next year, you know.
- Wait a minute.

15:58.082 --> 15:59.450
Why?

15:59.484 --> 16:01.486
I didn't like
what I saw tonight.

16:01.520 --> 16:04.422
What did you see tonight?
You saw me win tonight.

16:04.455 --> 16:05.824
Baby, look at your face.

16:05.857 --> 16:07.125
What are you talking about?

16:08.627 --> 16:10.762
Look at your face.

16:12.964 --> 16:14.432
Baby, what are you saying?

16:16.134 --> 16:18.036
Hey, baby,
can I ask you something?

16:18.069 --> 16:19.938
- What?
- What if I said this...

16:19.971 --> 16:22.040
"Look at your face.
Look at your face,"

16:22.073 --> 16:24.809
and then I started
crying? Okay?

16:26.310 --> 16:27.546
I'm sorry.

16:27.579 --> 16:29.013
Nah, it's-it's all good.

16:29.047 --> 16:30.515
- I'm sorry, but...
- It's good.

16:30.549 --> 16:31.916
...you fucking scared me.

16:31.950 --> 16:33.718
You can't fight
like that anymore.

16:33.752 --> 16:35.520
Baby, we... we won tonight.

16:35.554 --> 16:38.422
Yeah, but it's the way
you're fighting.

16:40.324 --> 16:42.527
- What are you talking about?
- Oh...

16:44.128 --> 16:46.264
The way I fight
bought us this house

16:46.297 --> 16:48.332
and bought you that
fucking beautiful dress.

16:48.366 --> 16:49.868
Yes, I know. I know.

16:49.901 --> 16:51.603
And it gave Leila
that fucking private school.

16:51.636 --> 16:54.038
- I know, baby. I know.
- All the shit in this house.

16:54.072 --> 16:56.040
Our fucking life,
that's what my fighting bought.

16:56.074 --> 16:57.776
But I want to enjoy it.

16:57.809 --> 16:59.811
