- What do you wanna talk about?
- Just whatever's going on in your head.

34:11.541 --> 34:14.911
I just... I just hope you're not
trying to do anything stupid

34:14.945 --> 34:16.679
like going after
Miguel or Hector.

34:16.714 --> 34:17.848
What do you wanna talk about?

34:17.880 --> 34:19.549
You wanna fucking talk now?

34:19.583 --> 34:21.918
Do you wanna fucking
talk to me now, huh?

34:21.952 --> 34:25.922
- Talk to me, you fucking pussy.
- Geez, I'm sorry!

34:25.956 --> 34:28.891
You were the one who's supposed
to fucking look after her.

34:28.926 --> 34:31.061
You were the one...
you were the one

34:31.094 --> 34:33.996
- that was supposed to look after her, huh?
- I'm sorry for Mo.

34:34.031 --> 34:36.667
I'm sorry...
and for your little girl.

34:36.699 --> 34:38.068
Kid, no, no, no.

34:38.101 --> 34:39.902
Get the fuck
out of my house.

34:39.937 --> 34:41.271
Get the fuck
out of my house!

34:41.304 --> 34:43.273
Get the fuck out!
Get the fuck out!

34:45.242 --> 34:47.577
Ain't fuckin' nothing
needin' nothing, man.

34:47.610 --> 34:49.880
No good fucking piece of shit.

35:23.346 --> 35:25.115
Hector!

35:25.148 --> 35:27.785
Hector ain't here.
Who is it?

35:27.818 --> 35:29.419
Open the door.

35:29.452 --> 35:31.054
Who is it?!

35:31.088 --> 35:33.008
I'm looking for Hector.
I got some money for him.

35:35.458 --> 35:37.127
I said move!

35:37.160 --> 35:39.329
You-you can give it to me.

35:39.362 --> 35:41.531
No, I need to g...
I need to give it to him.

35:45.168 --> 35:47.337
Uh, hold... hold on.

35:54.311 --> 35:56.113
Hector ain't here.

35:56.146 --> 35:58.081
Where is he?
Is he out with Miguel?

35:58.115 --> 36:01.051
I don't know.
You think he tells me shit?

36:01.084 --> 36:03.721
Yo, you gonna give me
money or not?

36:03.754 --> 36:05.723
- You got a hit?
- You his wife?

36:05.756 --> 36:07.691
I don't have to be.

36:07.725 --> 36:09.392
Not today.

36:10.660 --> 36:12.129
That ain't money.

36:12.162 --> 36:13.931
Yo, you got a hit?

36:13.964 --> 36:15.699
Where the fuck is he?

36:15.733 --> 36:17.735
- Hmm?
- Man...

36:19.703 --> 36:21.404
I got kids, man.

36:21.438 --> 36:22.740
Come on, baby.

36:22.773 --> 36:24.274
Come on.

36:24.307 --> 36:26.744
What are you doing?
Are you fucking crazy?

36:26.777 --> 36:28.812
Mommy's got you.

36:28.846 --> 36:30.513
I've got kids.

36:30.547 --> 36:32.315
Shit.

36:33.383 --> 36:34.718
Hey, I need a hit, though.

36:34.752 --> 36:36.019
Yo, you got a hit?

36:36.053 --> 36:39.089
Hey. Hey!

36:39.122 --> 36:40.523
I'm fucking talking to you!

36:40.557 --> 36:42.492
Where the fuck you going?!

36:45.295 --> 36:46.563
Fuck...

37:05.282 --> 37:07.084
They're all gonna keep you

37:07.117 --> 37:09.219
in that "Billy the Great"
bubble, you know?

37:09.252 --> 37:11.554
Billy! Billy! Billy!

37:11.588 --> 37:16.927
Billy "The Great"... Hope!

37:18.495 --> 37:20.163
Fuck!

37:26.469 --> 37:28.005
Hey, listen, Billy...

37:28.038 --> 37:31.074
you've got a lot
of money going out.

37:31.108 --> 37:32.575
You know,
with the mortgage

37:32.609 --> 37:34.845
and your friend Gabe's
legal fees

37:34.878 --> 37:36.379
and all your taxes
are due,

37:36.413 --> 37:38.315
including your property taxes.

37:38.348 --> 37:40.317
Uh, it's, uh,
starting to add up.

37:40.350 --> 37:43.453
Um, a lot of these
are overdue.

37:43.486 --> 37:44.855
Months, in fact.

37:44.888 --> 37:47.590
So... pay them.

37:47.624 --> 37:50.327
- With what?
- With my fucking money, Simon.

37:50.360 --> 37:51.962
That's why I'm here, Billy.

37:51.995 --> 37:53.563
The money,
it's drying up.

37:53.596 --> 37:56.299
Look, you gotta see
what's happening here.

37:56.333 --> 37:58.201
Um, you need to cut back.

37:58.235 --> 37:59.970
I mean, they've already
taken two of the cars.

38:00.003 --> 38:03.440
- What's it about, man?
- It... it's real simple.

38:03.473 --> 38:05.809
What's it about,
you-you taking my money?

38:05.843 --> 38:07.277
What?

38:07.310 --> 38:10.280
- You stealing from me, Simon?
- No.

38:10.313 --> 38:12.950
I'm-I'm just here
to help out.

38:12.983 --> 38:15.185
- I can take care of this if you want me to.
- Please.

38:15.218 --> 38:17.420
This is fine.

38:17.454 --> 38:19.122
- You can give me that and...
- Okay.

38:19.156 --> 38:20.390
You can leave this with me.

38:20.423 --> 38:21.892
I'll take care of it.

38:21.925 --> 38:23.760
Okay.

38:26.696 --> 38:28.698
Billy, I just want to say
I'm really sorry.

38:28.731 --> 38:31.734
About everything.

38:33.971 --> 38:35.672
Hey, look, Billy.

38:35.705 --> 38:37.340
You need this.

38:37.374 --> 38:39.476
This solves all your problems.

38:39.509 --> 38:41.845
- What is that?
- It's the contract.

38:41.879 --> 38:44.714
To fight Turay.
Look, I'm not gonna pretend

38:44.747 --> 38:46.649
I... I know the pain
you're going through.

38:46.683 --> 38:48.451
But I do know for you
to get through it,

38:48.485 --> 38:50.153
you're gonna have
to get back in that ring.

38:50.187 --> 38:51.554
No, Mo doesn't want me
to sign that.

38:51.588 --> 38:53.390
No, Mo didn't want you
to sign it then.

38:53.423 --> 38:55.325
Now she would want you
to actually sign the contract.

38:55.358 --> 38:56.693
Why you say that?

38:56.726 --> 38:58.395
Billy, every time
I seen you fight,

38:58.428 --> 39:00.330
you climb in there alone.

39:00.363 --> 39:02.966
Every time you bled,
you bled your blood.

39:03.000 --> 39:04.801
When you sat down on that stool
and it felt like death

39:04.834 --> 39:07.037
and you thought you couldn't
get up, but you got up?

39:07.070 --> 39:08.872
You did that.

39:08.906 --> 39:11.975
You need to get back
to that.

39:12.009 --> 39:14.511
You want Leila to grow up
the way you grew up?

39:14.544 --> 39:17.380
You want her in the streets?

39:17.414 --> 39:19.449
It's a three-fight deal, Billy.

39:19.482 --> 39:21.451
Got to get back to doing
what we do, man.

39:21.484 --> 39:25.222
When you're in the ring, you're gonna
feel different. I'm telling you.

39:26.789 --> 39:29.259
It's not about
contracts, right?

39:30.293 --> 39:31.995
It's about family.

39:32.029 --> 39:33.669
I don't know what I'd do
without you, man.

39:33.696 --> 39:35.532
You ain't gotta worry
about that, man.

39:50.914 --> 39:53.650
Nobody would've
expected Kalil Turay

39:53.683 --> 39:57.854
to have his way throughout
the fight against Billy Hope.

39:57.887 --> 40:00.457
Billy, put them goddamn
hands up now!

40:00.490 --> 40:02.792
Hope fighting in the wake

40:02.825 --> 40:05.062
- of his wife's unexpected death.
- Get off that rope!

40:05.095 --> 40:06.763
No aggression...

40:06.796 --> 40:10.167
simply a will to continue
taking punishment...

40:10.200 --> 40:11.368
Get off them goddamn ropes!

40:11.401 --> 40:13.003
...and to allow Turay

40:13.036 --> 40:15.238
to pound him with both fists

40:15.272 --> 40:16.673
to the body and the head.

40:16.706 --> 40:19.076
Ending it, now!

40:19.109 --> 40:23.346
But it's been a bloodletting
from the first bell onward.

40:23.380 --> 40:26.516
Yes!

40:26.549 --> 40:28.885
Hope finally gets in a right hand.

40:28.918 --> 40:31.288
Those have been
few and far between.

40:31.321 --> 40:33.256
- By and large,
- Control your fighter!

40:33.290 --> 40:38.628
It was a beat-down by Kalil
Turay, who appears to have scored

40:38.661 --> 40:41.965
an upset victory
over Billy Hope

40:41.999 --> 40:44.901
and perhaps has put
the finishing touches

40:44.934 --> 40:46.769
on Hope's great career.

40:46.803 --> 40:49.506
Focus, you hear me?
Huh? Billy, listen to me, man.

40:49.539 --> 40:51.908
I'm not gonna watch this. I'm not
gonna watch this happen to you, man.

40:51.941 --> 40:53.610
I'm not gonna watch
this happen to us.

40:53.643 --> 40:55.278
Billy, if you don't
show me something here,

40:55.312 --> 40:56.713
I'm gonna call it.
That's it. You hear me?

40:56.746 --> 40:58.548
We're done.
Wake up, champ.

40:58.581 --> 41:00.850
Don't call it, man.
No, don't call it.

41:00.883 --> 41:02.619
What the fuck
are we doing here, huh?

41:02.652 --> 41:04.254
I gotta end
this shit, Billy.

41:04.287 --> 41:06.023
You hear me?

41:06.056 --> 41:08.291
I'm not gonna watch this shit
happen to you, man, all right?

41:08.325 --> 41:09.859
Remember when we were done,

41:09.892 --> 41:11.728
when we were done,
you used to fight?

41:11.761 --> 41:13.997
Like, get up, get up.
Let's go.

41:14.031 --> 41:15.932
Come on, champ.
Let's go.

41:17.667 --> 41:19.636
He keep looking
out the ring for Maureen.

41:19.669 --> 41:21.938
He's losing
his fucking mind, bro.

41:23.506 --> 41:25.008
Seconds out.

41:25.042 --> 41:26.443
This guy is done.

41:26.476 --> 41:28.211
He's not the champ anymore.
Finish him.

41:28.245 --> 41:31.114
Hands up. Fight back.
Focus. Come on.

41:31.148 --> 41:32.915
Corner ready?

41:59.876 --> 42:02.011
Get the damn hands up,
Billy! Now!

42:10.687 --> 42:12.655
Oh, man!

42:21.064 --> 42:24.267
Billy Hope has
refused to compete here tonight.

42:24.301 --> 42:25.902
...fuck you!

42:25.935 --> 42:29.172
Another giant shot from Turay

42:29.206 --> 42:31.108
and the referee
is gonna stop it.

42:31.141 --> 42:33.042
- It's gonna be the end of that.
- It's over.

42:33.076 --> 42:34.711
No, don't call it.
No, don't call it.

42:34.744 --> 42:36.479
- That's it, it's over.
- No...!

42:36.513 --> 42:38.481
And Hope headbutts the referee!

42:40.750 --> 42:44.020
A horrible moment
as a final postscript

42:44.053 --> 42:47.557
to what has been a horrible
night for Billy Hope,

42:47.590 --> 42:49.592
and a career which produced
so many thrills...

42:49.626 --> 42:52.962
- I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
- ...and so much joyous glory,

42:52.995 --> 42:58.168
appears to have ended
ignominiously here tonight.

43:17.954 --> 43:19.689
Eli?

43:24.361 --> 43:25.895
Eli?

43:28.030 --> 43:29.699
Is Jordan here?

43:42.345 --> 43:44.681
Is anybody still here?

43:48.050 --> 43:50.487
You headbutt a referee, man.

43:50.520 --> 43:52.355
What the fuck kind of shit
was that, man?

43:52.389 --> 43:56.125
Broke his nose. Shattered his
motherfucking cheekbone.

43:56.159 --> 43:58.060
What got into you, man?

43:58.094 --> 44:01.164
We did the biggest deal
that we ever did, Billy,

44:01.198 --> 44:03.200
and you fucked it off, man.

44:03.233 --> 44:06.002
It'll be a year before your
suspension is up for review,

44:06.035 --> 44:08.705
which means zero income. The fine
for the assault on the referee

44:08.738 --> 44:10.907
will be in the six figures.
He's suing you

44:10.940 --> 44:13.075
for lost wages
and emotional trauma.

44:13.109 --> 44:15.478
They're freezing all your
bank accounts immediately,

44:15.512 --> 44:18.581
and to top that off the networks are
suing us for breach of contract, man.

44:18.615 --> 44:20.617
Listen...

44:20.650 --> 44:23.553
you're gonna have to sell the
house to cover the debt.

44:23.586 --> 44:27.190
No, I don't wanna sell the house, man.
I'm not selling the house.

44:27.224 --> 44:29.859
- That's Leila's home.
- You don't have a choice, Billy.

44:29.892 --> 44:32.762
If you don't, it's gonna
get repossessed anyway.

44:32.795 --> 44:34.731
- This is some serious shit.
- No, no, no.

44:34.764 --> 44:38.235
I'll just train with Eli and then
we'll get ready for the next fight.

44:38.268 --> 44:40.803
I'm not even sure trainers
will take you on right now.

44:40.837 --> 44:42.839
What? I don't need another trainer.
I can just use...

44:42.872 --> 44:45.174
Eli's working
with another fighter.

44:45.208 --> 44:47.910
- Who? Who is he? Who is he?
- Miguel Escobar.

44:47.944 --> 44:51.281
- Are you working with him, too?
- Yeah.

44:51.314 --> 44:53.816
Billy, you know if
it makes money, it makes sense.

44:55.752 --> 44:57.954
- Oh, you...
- It's just business, Billy.

44:57.987 --> 45:01.624
I know you miss Maureen.
I miss Maureen, too, man.

45:01.658 --> 45:04.661
Shit, if she was here, she'd
be disgusted with you, man.

45:04.694 --> 45:07.330
We need you to pull yourself together.
You need help, Billy.

45:07.364 --> 45:09.532
Don't talk about
my wife that way.

45:14.471 --> 45:15.705
I fucking quit.
Fuck you.

45:15.738 --> 45:17.374
Can't do this anymore, Billy.

45:17.407 --> 45:18.641
Fuck outta my way.

45:19.676 --> 45:22.579
Scatter like roaches.

45:24.447 --> 45:27.047
Y'all follow him, make sure he don't
break no shit on the way out.

45:32.121 --> 45:33.490
Just a bunch of roaches.

45:33.523 --> 45:36.025
Now I fuckin' wrote you off.

46:23.139 --> 46:25.875
Baby, let's go home.
Let's go home.

46:25.908 --> 46:29.546
Let it go.
Baby, baby, stop it... stop...

47:05.448 --> 47:07.417
I'm sorry.

47:11.120 --> 47:13.790
I'm sorry.

47:20.296 --> 47:22.298
Dad?

47:26.369 --> 47:28.438
Dad?

47:28.471 --> 47:30.873
Dad! Daddy!

47:30.907 --> 47:32.709
Daddy, what happened?

47:32.742 --> 47:35.044
Daddy! Daddy!

47:35.077 --> 47:38.214
Somebody help me!
Somebody!

47:38.247 --> 47:40.116
Mr. Hope,
what did you take, sir?

47:40.149 --> 47:43.986
What did you take, Mr. Hope?
What'd you take?

47:44.020 --> 47:46.989
What kind of medicine,
Mr. Hope? What did you take?

47:47.023 --> 47:49.459
Mr. Hope?
What did you take, sir?

47:49.492 --> 47:51.628
Leila...
Where's my baby?

47:51.661 --> 47:55.231
Your daughter's fine. She's the one who
called 911. You were in an accident.

47:55.264 --> 47:57.066
- There's people looking after her.
- Leila?

47:57.099 --> 47:59.936
No, no, no. No, no.
She needs me.

47:59.969 --> 48:01.904
We found you with
a loaded weapon, Mr. Hope,

48:01.938 --> 48:03.973
under the influence,
with a minor present.

48:04.006 --> 48:06.342
Where's my baby? Leila?

48:06.375 --> 48:09.879
Where's Leila?
I gotta get outta here.

48:09.912 --> 48:12.214
Your daughter's with Child Services.
They're looking after her right now.

48:12.248 --> 48:13.816
- No, no, no, no...
- Everything's okay.

48:13.850 --> 48:15.552
No, no, no. No!

48:15.585 --> 48:17.454
- They're looking after her.
- We just lost the IV.

48:17.487 --> 48:19.589
- Get him down. Get his legs.
- No, no, no, no!

48:19.622 --> 48:21.357
- No!
- You got him?

48:21.390 --> 48:23.025
Lay back for me, Mr. Hope.
You're gonna be just fine.

48:23.059 --> 48:24.994
- No!
- Come on, just breathe.

48:27.564 --> 48:30.066
- Lay back. Everything's all right.
- Breathe.

48:30.099 --> 48:31.834
Just... just chill out
for a second.

48:31.868 --> 48:33.736
You're gonna be okay,
Mr. Hope.

48:33.770 --> 48:35.271
Just take a deep breath for me.

48:35.304 --> 48:37.073
Gonna be fine, all right?

48:38.475 --> 48:40.109
Gonna be fine.

48:40.142 --> 48:42.344
You're gonna be fine, Mr. Hope.

48:42.378 --> 48:43.746
Just relax.

48:47.249 --> 48:49.185
Maureen... no...

48:49.218 --> 48:51.387
no... I was...

48:59.862 --> 49:01.163
Maureen...

49:12.875 --> 49:15.778
Okay, he wants his copies.
I'll provide that.

49:15.812 --> 49:17.780
I promise.
By day's end.

49:17.814 --> 49:19.716
- If it's okay with you.
- All right.

49:19.749 --> 49:22.284
What about
the, uh... this evidence?

49:22.318 --> 49:23.853
Daddy.

49:23.886 --> 49:27.023
- Baby!
- Sit down, Mr. Hope.

49:28.925 --> 49:30.459
I just want to hug my dad.

49:30.493 --> 49:32.461
Mr. Korman,
get your client, please.

49:32.495 --> 49:34.030
Sit down.
Sit down, Billy.

49:34.063 --> 49:36.499
Thank you.
We're ready to begin.

49:36.533 --> 49:38.868
The matter this morning
is provisional custody

49:38.901 --> 49:41.137
of Leila Rae Hope, a minor...

49:41.170 --> 49:43.906
- When can I get her out?
- Don't interrupt, Mr. Hope.

49:43.940 --> 49:47.009
The child has no other
family, is that right?

49:47.043 --> 49:50.146
Uh, no, Your Honor.
Uh, both my client

49:50.179 --> 49:52.181
and his wife came up
through the system.

49:52.214 --> 49:54.383
I see.
So that's why

49:54.416 --> 49:56.953
these circumstances are a little
bit more painful for you.

49:56.986 --> 49:59.756
I want my daughter back.
I'm her father.

49:59.789 --> 50:01.791
Unfortunately,
that's not enough.

50:03.159 --> 50:05.261
This court is aware of
the tragedy

50:05.294 --> 50:07.730
your family
has suffered, Mr. Hope.

50:07.764 --> 50:09.465
Nonetheless,
you have chosen

50:09.498 --> 50:12.334
to demonstrate alarming
and dangerous behaviors,

50:12.368 --> 50:14.837
while having
custody of your daughter.

50:14.871 --> 50:19.308
Loaded weapons,
alcohol, violence...

50:19.341 --> 50:22.579
Mr. Hope will follow a case plan
that the court has designed.

50:22.612 --> 50:25.447
Said plan will include
individual counseling,

50:25.481 --> 50:28.618
as well as sobriety
and anger management classes.

50:28.651 --> 50:33.522
And I order said child remanded into
the care of the Family Services,

50:33.556 --> 50:35.958
until which time
the father can demonstrate

50:35.992 --> 50:39.095
the abilities to perform duties
of a responsible parent.

50:39.128 --> 50:41.297
- What?
- Parties back in 30 days

50:41.330 --> 50:43.099
- 30 days?!
- ...for a progress hearing.

50:43.132 --> 50:45.001
What the fuck does that mean?
30 days?

50:45.034 --> 50:47.536
- Watch your language.
- 30 days is bullshit, man.

50:47.570 --> 50:49.338
- That's bullshit!
- I will find you in contempt.

50:49.371 --> 50:51.173
Please, please,
I don't want to...

50:51.207 --> 50:52.842
- I'm sorry, Your Honor.
- My last warning.

50:52.875 --> 50:54.644
I don't want to.
Please, Daddy!

50:54.677 --> 50:56.813
- Billy! Come on! Billy!
- Take the child out, please.

50:56.846 --> 50:58.214
Please, I want
to stay with you!

50:58.247 --> 51:01.017
Let me just give
my daughter a hug!

51:01.050 --> 51:02.619
No, no, no...

51:02.652 --> 51:04.721
Daddy! Please!

51:04.754 --> 51:07.489
- He wants to see his daughter!
- Please, Dad...

51:07.523 --> 51:09.926
- Daddy!
- That's not necessary.

51:09.959 --> 51:12.294
No! I want to live with you!

51:12.328 --> 51:13.763
Please!

51:13.796 --> 51:15.865
- Get down there.
- Daddy! Daddy!

51:15.898 --> 51:18.935
Mr. Hope, that's enough.
I will hold you in contempt.

51:45.494 --> 51:48.965
Everything goes to auction.

51:53.636 --> 51:56.372
Hey, Evan, help me out
with this, will you?

51:56.405 --> 52:00.076
That'll go inside
the truck, towards the back.

52:03.479 --> 52:06.448
- Auction's tomorrow.
- No, it's all going to auction.

52:06.482 --> 52:07.583
Sorry, champ.

53:04.506 --> 53:07.376
Yeah, it's just a house, yeah?

53:09.378 --> 53:13.049
Hey, yo, thanks for, uh...
thanks for taking me.

53:13.082 --> 53:14.751
No, Billy.

53:14.784 --> 53:17.053
You know, I-I can't
really pay you right now.

53:17.086 --> 53:20.757
Well, fuck you.

53:20.790 --> 53:22.124
No, I don't want
to get paid.

