two-point round to get him over the hump.

01:55:21.106 --> 01:55:23.075
Whether he won
the fight or not,

01:55:23.108 --> 01:55:24.843
he'll have
tremendous satisfaction

01:55:24.877 --> 01:55:28.447
from having knocked
Miguel Escobar down.

01:55:28.481 --> 01:55:31.416
