Jimmy Lennon Jr.

01:55:31.450 --> 01:55:34.520
To find out who's the winner.

01:55:34.553 --> 01:55:37.055
Ladies and gentlemen,

01:55:37.089 --> 01:55:39.492
after 12 rounds of action,

01:55:39.525 --> 01:55:41.694
