We did it, baby.

01:57:12.250 --> 01:57:14.853
What an amazing
moment of redemption

01:57:14.887 --> 01:57:16.755
for Billy Hope.

01:57:16.789 --> 01:57:18.523
Hey, baby...

01:57:20.225 --> 01:57:22.728
I'm ready.
