Hey, T. Come here.

01:57:32.470 --> 01:57:33.972
What?

01:57:34.006 --> 01:57:36.241
- It's your belt.
- It's for you, man.

01:57:36.274 --> 01:57:37.743
No, no, no.
That's-that's yours.

01:57:37.776 --> 01:57:39.011
Hey, hey, it's
too heavy, man!

01:57:39.044 --> 01:57:40.512
No, no. No, no... no, no.

