- Hmm?
- I was scared for you.

01:58:11.810 --> 01:58:13.946
- Aw.
- It was so scary.

01:58:13.979 --> 01:58:17.850
Aw, baby,
you're so brave.

01:58:17.883 --> 01:58:19.451
You guys take care
of each other.

01:58:23.588 --> 01:58:25.490
I love you, Daddy.

01:58:26.992 --> 01:58:29.461
Yeah, baby.

01:58:32.297 --> 01:58:36.068
