I was so worried for you.

01:58:59.291 --> 01:59:00.558
Mm.

01:59:02.828 --> 01:59:04.830
Come here.

01:59:19.678 --> 01:59:20.779
Back up. Back up.

01:59:20.813 --> 01:59:22.280
Give the man some room.

